body_html:
@TethysSun: sounds for me like a problem with your environment. I am sorry, but I cannot help you with OSX.

Just in case, try to uninstall and reinstall wheel. Also check which python variable you used when you run "./configure". Maybe you want to change it to the python3 binary.
